  "title": "Temp Lab Technician (West) #HHW",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>1. Responsible for testing of finished goods to ensure they meet technical specifications.</p>\n<p>2. Receive, label and store samples with relevant safety &amp; hazard information.</p>\n<p>3. Maintains laboratory equipment and inventory levels for laboratory supplies and consumables for smooth operation of laboratory.</p>\n<p>4. Responsible for the accuracy, integrity and reliability of laboratory test results generated.</p>\n<p>5. Execute all duties faithfully and responsibly in accordance to written procedures and to immediately report all observations of Quality and Safety non-conformances.</p>\n<p>6. Ensure all activities are in continuous compliance with QEHSMS in designated areas of responsibilities.</p>\n<p>7. Perform and assume other duties and responsibilities as may be required by the QA Manager</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested candidates please to <a href=\"mailto:wendykhoo@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\">wendykhoo@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p>\n<p>Wendy Khoo Hui Wen - R1761665</p>\n<p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 99C4599</p>",
